er can\r\nalways accept the return irrespective of the policy.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;If Seller\r\ndisagrees a return request, Buyer can file a dispute under the Buyer Protection\r\nProgram.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;In the event\r\nthe Seller accepts the return request raised by the Buyer, Buyer will have to\r\nreturn the product and then the refund shall be credited to the Buyers account.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;We encourage\r\nthe Buyer to review the listing before making the purchase decision. In case\r\nBuyer orders a wrong item, Buyer shall not be entitled to any return/refund.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;Refund without\r\nshipment collection - Seller has agreed to refund the buyer without expecting\r\nthe original shipment back) &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;Refund after\r\nshipment collection - Seller has agreed to wait for the logistics team to\r\ncollect the shipment from the buyer before refunding)&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;Replace\r\nwithout shipment collection - Seller has agreed to replace the order without\r\nexpecting the original shipment back&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;line-height:normal&quot;&gt;Further for\r\nreturns being made by Buyer to the Seller of the product, the following\r\nparameters needs to be ensured by the Buyer:&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;mso-element:para-